name: AUDI E-TRON GT PRESTIGE
description: The Audi e-tron GT Prestige is a high-performance electric vehicle that boasts a stunning 522 horsepower with boost mode engaged, allowing it to accelerate from 0-60 MPH in just a few seconds. This luxurious sedan features a wide stance with flowing lines, a fixed panoramic roof, and Matrix-design LED headlights that cast distinctive illumination. The interior is crafted with a passion for design and luxury, featuring 14-way power-adjustable sport seats wrapped in Dinamica and leatherette, a flat-bottom steering wheel, and available multi-color LED contour and ambient lighting.
rate: The overall rating of the Audi E-Tron GT Prestige is around 7.9 out of 10

name: AUDI Q4 SPORTBACK E-TRON
description: The Audi Q4 Sportback e-tron is a fully electric SUV that features dual electric motors providing standard quattro all-wheel drive and boasts up to 335 HP. This luxurious vehicle offers a spacious interior that rivals any luxury-class car, with advanced technology features like an available augmented reality head-up display and a 10.1-inch MMI touch display. The Q4 Sportback e-tron also offers an EPA-estimated range of up to 258 miles on a single charge, making it an ideal choice for daily driving and long road trips.
rate: The overall rating of the Audi Q4 Sportback E-Tron is around 8.1 out of 10

name: AUDI Q5 PRESTIGE
description: The Audi Q5 Prestige is the top trim level, offering luxurious features such as ventilated front seats, heated rear seats, and a Head-Up display. It also comes with advanced technology features like a 12.3-inch virtual cockpit, Bang & Olufsen premium sound system, and a 360-degree camera system. Additionally, the Prestige trim includes exterior enhancements like 20-inch alloy wheels and a unique rear diffuser.
rate: The overall rating of the Audi Q5 Prestige is around 8.8 out of 10

name: AUDI Q6 E-TRON PREMIUM PLUS
description: The Audi Q6 e-tron Premium Plus is a premium mid-size all-electric SUV that boasts an EPA-estimated range of 307 miles with standard wheels. It features a 456-hp dual-motor powertrain with all-wheel drive, providing swift acceleration and responsive handling. Inside, the Premium Plus trim offers luxurious amenities, including a 10.1-inch touchscreen, heated and ventilated front seats, and a premium Bang & Olufsen sound system.
rate: The overall rating of the Audi Q6 E-Tron Premium Plus is around 8.4 out of 10

name: AUDI Q8 E-TRON PRESTIGE
description: The Audi Q8 E-Tron Prestige is a luxurious electric SUV that offers a spacious interior, advanced technology features, and a comfortable ride, with a range of up to 305 miles on a single charge. It features a premium interior with heated and ventilated seats, a panoramic sunroof, and a 12.3-inch virtual cockpit display. The Prestige trim also adds exclusive features such as a heads-up display, a 360-degree camera system, and a Bang & Olufsen premium sound system.
rate: The overall rating of the Audi Q8 E-Tron Prestige is around 3 out of 5 stars

name: AUDI Q8 SPORTBACK E-TRON PRESTIGE
description: The Audi Q8 Sportback E-Tron Prestige is a luxury electric SUV that combines sleek design, advanced technology, and impressive performance, featuring a spacious interior, ample cargo space, and a range of up to 305 miles on a single charge. It boasts a powerful dual-electric motor setup, producing 402 horsepower and 486 lb-ft of torque, and comes equipped with premium features like a 12.3-inch virtual cockpit, 10.1-inch infotainment screen, and advanced safety features. With its unique blend of style, comfort, and sustainability, the Q8 Sportback E-Tron Prestige is an attractive option for those seeking a high-end electric vehicle.
rate: The overall rating of the Audi Q8 Sportback E-Tron Prestige is around 8.5 out of 10

name: AUDI RS E-TRON GT PRESTIGE
description: The Audi RS e-tron GT Prestige is a high-performance electric grand tourer that boasts a luxurious interior, advanced technology features, and exceptional acceleration, with a 0-60 mph time of just 3.3 seconds. Powered by two electric motors producing 590 horsepower and 464 lb-ft of torque, it offers a range of up to 232 miles on a single charge. With its sleek design, premium materials, and advanced safety features, the RS e-tron GT Prestige is a flagship model that embodies Audi's commitment to innovation and performance.
rate: The overall rating of the Audi RS e-tron GT Prestige is around 8.5 out of 10
